title: Macgo Blu-ray Player for Windows v2.16.5.2096 [deepstatus]
description:
Macgo Blu-ray Player for Windows v2.16.5.2096 [deepstatus]

Macgo Windows Blu-ray Player is an excellent Blu-ray player
software for Windows. It can play Blu-ray Disc, Blu-ray ISO file,
and Blu-ray (BDMV) folders on all Windows operating systems,
including Windows 10. Windows 10 doesn't have native support of DVD
or Blu-ray playback. Macgo got you all covered.




Key Features:

Excellent Blu-ray player software for Windows-based computers
Directly play Blu-ray Discs and Blu-ray ISO files without conversion
Easily play Blu-ray folders (BDMV folders)
Perfect output up to 1080p High Definition quality without loss for
fantastic home cinema entertainment
Audio and video media files sharable between Windows and iOS devices
Worked as long as devices are connected in the same Wi-Fi environment
or Home Network
Play Blu-ray and other media formats on iOS devices anywhere and anytime
Unique Macgo technology, easy to operate

Fully support DTS5.1 and provide super high quality of stereo output
without loss for Windows. This is the first ever program to do that
Initiative support DTS7.1 Passthrough
With DTS5.1 audio system, Macgo Windows Blu-ray Player provides
the best-in-class audio output for Windows
Let you enjoy fantastic home theater entertainment.
